<h2 class="heading colr">Host a Blood Donation Camp</h2>

<p class="txt"></p>



<p><strong>I. Selecting an area</strong><strong> for blood
donation:</strong></p>
<p>A minimum of 75 to 100 people should be in the
organization/institute that you plan to organize a blood donation camp.
Some of the places you can try are:</p>
<p>- Colleges/Institutes</p>
<p>- Corporate organizations/companies</p>
<p>- Religious organizations</p>
<p>- Banks</p>
<p>- Markets/malls</p>
<p>- Factories</p>
<p></p>
